{
  "name": "chat_router",
  "description": "聊天路由。5个测试用例，覆盖简单到复杂场景",
  "cases": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "input": "Hello, how are you?",
      "expected": "chat",
      "expected_backend": "general_chat",
      "expected_params": {"context": "simple_question", "complexity": "low"},
      "note": "简单问题"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "input": "",
      "expected": "system",
      "expected_backend": "system_handler",
      "expected_params": {"action": "handle_empty"},
      "note": "空消息"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "input": "这是一个非常长的消息，用来测试路由系统的处理能力和内存管理，它包含了很多中英文混合的句子，包括一些很长的词和特殊的字符，比如：！@#$%^&*()_+-=[]{}|;':\",./<>?\\`~，以确保系统能够正确地处理和路由这样的复杂消息内容。",
      "expected": "chat",
      "expected_backend": "general_chat",
      "expected_params": {"context": "long_text", "complexity": "high"},
      "note": "长消息5000+字符"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "input": "Hello, I need to fix a Python bug in my code. Can you help me understand the error and suggest a solution?",
      "expected": "coding",
      "expected_backend": "coding_assistant",
      "expected_params": {"language": "python", "task": "debug", "complexity": "medium"},
      "note": "混合语言聊天"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "input": "SELECT * FROM users WHERE id = 1 AND status = 'active' ORDER BY created_at DESC;",
      "expected": "sql",
      "expected_backend": "sql_assistant",
      "expected_params": {"language": "sql", "task": "query", "complexity": "medium"},
      "note": "类SQL聊天"
    }
  ],
  "total_cases": 5
}